originalText.text: I love going to this store for easy pick up items. The prices are great the store is always clean. The owner is so friendly and attentive it's a warm family atmosphere. They make hot and cold sandwiches and they are to die for. Milk ,cheese, eggs  and cereal bread fresh fruit and muffins! Hygienic needs as well. Be sure to stop in and say hello.
